Rip notes: downsampled opening and ending FMVs 

Awakening shipwrecked just after a meteor collides with a remote biotech research island, you begin to discover
an incontrollable madness unleashed in the meteor's wake. As one secret uncovers another, you piece together a
horrifying revelation that could lead to the end of life on Earth.
* Solve puzzles and avoid hazards in 7 areas and 230 locations.
* Adjustable camera as you swim, climb, fight, blast...
* Master awesome hand-to-hand moves and 22 weapons.


After a meteor strikes the tropical shores of Dinosaur Island, many strange events have been taking place. As Eliot Ballade, an elite member of ESER (Emergency Sea Evacuation and Rescue), you will rely on your wits and strength to help you solve the mystery of this island and come out alive. BLUE STINGER uses the innovative Follow Cam system to lead you through all 230 cinematic environments your character will travel through. You will have to solve puzzles, discover secrets, and battle monsters as you try to uncover the truth. With over 50 monsters and over 20 weapons, this game offers a huge variety of gameplay. Arm yourself with anything from a bazooka to a napalm launcher, and show those monsters who the boss really is. This game is a must buy for anyone who loves a good adventure.